{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":632,"text":"I'd like to introduce you to an organism:"},{"time":3737,"text":"a slime mold, Physarum polycephalum."},{"time":7193,"text":"It's a mold with an identity\ncrisis, because it's not a mold,"},{"time":10015,"text":"so let's get that straight to start with."},{"time":11945,"text":"It is one of 700 known slime molds"},{"time":14481,"text":"belonging to the kingdom of the amoeba."},{"time":16618,"text":"It is a single-celled organism, a cell,"},{"time":19241,"text":"that joins together with other cells"},{"time":21481,"text":"to form a mass super-cell"},{"time":23713,"text":"to maximize its resources."},{"time":25953,"text":"So within a slime mold you might find thousands"},{"time":28113,"text":"or millions of nuclei,"},{"time":30360,"text":"all sharing a cell wall,"},{"time":32121,"text":"all operating as one entity."},{"time":35229,"text":"In its natural habitat,"},{"time":36833,"text":"you might find the slime mold foraging in woodlands,"},{"time":39629,"text":"eating rotting vegetation,"},{"time":43330,"text":"but you might equally find it"},{"time":44870,"text":"in research laboratories,"},{"time":46412,"text":"classrooms, and even artists' studios."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50614,"text":"I first came across the slime\nmold about five years ago."},{"time":53549,"text":"A microbiologist friend of mine"},{"time":55106,"text":"gave me a petri dish with a little yellow blob in it"},{"time":58230,"text":"and told me to go home and play with it."},{"time":61238,"text":"The only instructions I was given,"},{"time":63245,"text":"that it likes it dark and damp"},{"time":65029,"text":"and its favorite food is porridge oats."},{"time":69360,"text":"I'm an artist who's worked for many years"},{"time":71378,"text":"with biology, with scientific processes,"},{"time":74225,"text":"so living material is not uncommon for me."},{"time":77236,"text":"I've worked with plants, bacteria,"},{"time":79341,"text":"cuttlefish, fruit flies."},{"time":80860,"text":"So I was keen to get my new collaborator home"},{"time":83462,"text":"to see what it could do."},{"time":84838,"text":"So I took it home and I watched."},{"time":88040,"text":"I fed it a varied diet."},{"time":90810,"text":"I observed as it networked."},{"time":92734,"text":"It formed a connection between food sources."},{"time":95010,"text":"I watched it leave a trail behind it,"},{"time":97848,"text":"indicating where it had been."},{"time":99607,"text":"And I noticed that when it was\nfed up with one petri dish,"},{"time":102555,"text":"it would escape and find a better home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105534,"text":"I captured my observations"},{"time":107262,"text":"through time-lapse photography."},{"time":109022,"text":"Slime mold grows at about one centimeter an hour,"},{"time":111860,"text":"so it's not really ideal for live viewing"},{"time":114441,"text":"unless there's some form of\nreally extreme meditation,"},{"time":117294,"text":"but through the time lapse,"},{"time":119822,"text":"I could observe some really interesting behaviors."},{"time":122918,"text":"For instance, having fed on a nice pile of oats,"},{"time":126418,"text":"the slime mold goes off to explore new territories"},{"time":130862,"text":"in different directions simultaneously."},{"time":133594,"text":"When it meets itself,"},{"time":135833,"text":"it knows it's already there,"},{"time":137700,"text":"it recognizes it's there,"},{"time":139654,"text":"and instead retreats back"},{"time":141201,"text":"and grows in other directions."},{"time":144881,"text":"I was quite impressed by this feat,"},{"time":147205,"text":"at how what was essentially\njust a bag of cellular slime"},{"time":150755,"text":"could somehow map its territory,"},{"time":153985,"text":"know itself, and move with seeming intention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157457,"text":"I found countless scientific studies,"},{"time":161110,"text":"research papers, journal articles,"},{"time":163155,"text":"all citing incredible work with this one organism,"},{"time":167379,"text":"and I'm going to share a few of those with you."},{"time":169343,"text":"For example, a team in Hokkaido University in Japan"},{"time":172303,"text":"filled a maze with slime mold."},{"time":174335,"text":"It joined together and formed a mass cell."},{"time":176431,"text":"They introduced food at two points,"},{"time":178783,"text":"oats of course,"},{"time":179981,"text":"and it formed a connection"},{"time":181627,"text":"between the food."},{"time":183041,"text":"It retracted from empty areas and dead ends."},{"time":185525,"text":"There are four possible routes through this maze,"},{"time":188335,"text":"yet time and time again,"},{"time":190440,"text":"the slime mold established the shortest"},{"time":192607,"text":"and the most efficient route."},{"time":195060,"text":"Quite clever."},{"time":196311,"text":"The conclusion from their experiment"},{"time":198050,"text":"was that the slime mold had\na primitive form of intelligence."},{"time":201047,"text":"Another study exposed cold air at\nregular intervals to the slime mold."},{"time":204910,"text":"It didn't like it. It doesn't like it cold."},{"time":207255,"text":"It doesn't like it dry."},{"time":208448,"text":"They did this at repeat intervals,"},{"time":210563,"text":"and each time, the slime mold"},{"time":212221,"text":"slowed down its growth in response."},{"time":215351,"text":"However, at the next interval,"},{"time":217195,"text":"the researchers didn't put the cold air on,"},{"time":220019,"text":"yet the slime mold slowed down in anticipation"},{"time":223313,"text":"of it happening."},{"time":224649,"text":"It somehow knew that it was about the time"},{"time":227175,"text":"for the cold air that it didn't like."},{"time":229131,"text":"The conclusion from their experiment"},{"time":230820,"text":"was that the slime mold was able to learn."},{"time":234090,"text":"A third experiment:"},{"time":235321,"text":"the slime mold was invited"},{"time":237088,"text":"to explore a territory covered in oats."},{"time":241280,"text":"It fans out in a branching pattern."},{"time":244327,"text":"As it goes, each food node it finds,"},{"time":246975,"text":"it forms a network, a connection to,"},{"time":249675,"text":"and keeps foraging."},{"time":251423,"text":"After 26 hours, it established"},{"time":253864,"text":"quite a firm network"},{"time":255481,"text":"between the different oats."},{"time":257271,"text":"Now there's nothing remarkable in this"},{"time":259091,"text":"until you learn that the center oat that it started from"},{"time":261503,"text":"represents the city of Tokyo,"},{"time":263517,"text":"and the surrounding oats are\nsuburban railway stations."},{"time":267583,"text":"The slime mold had replicated"},{"time":270064,"text":"the Tokyo transport network"},{"time":272480,"text":"— (Laughter) —"},{"time":274135,"text":"a complex system developed over time"},{"time":277130,"text":"by community dwellings, civil\nengineering, urban planning."},{"time":281030,"text":"What had taken us well over 100 years"},{"time":283303,"text":"took the slime mold just over a day."},{"time":286469,"text":"The conclusion from their experiment"},{"time":288122,"text":"was that the slime mold can form efficient networks"},{"time":290632,"text":"and solve the traveling salesman problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293255,"text":"It is a biological computer."},{"time":295519,"text":"As such, it has been mathematically modeled,"},{"time":298143,"text":"algorithmically analyzed."},{"time":299804,"text":"It's been sonified, replicated, simulated."},{"time":302509,"text":"World over, teams of researchers"},{"time":305479,"text":"are decoding its biological principles"},{"time":308449,"text":"to understand its computational rules"},{"time":310590,"text":"and applying that learning\nto the fields of electronics,"},{"time":312844,"text":"programming and robotics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315080,"text":"So the question is,"},{"time":317234,"text":"how does this thing work?"},{"time":319254,"text":"It doesn't have a central nervous system."},{"time":321414,"text":"It doesn't have a brain,"},{"time":323112,"text":"yet it can perform behaviors"},{"time":324940,"text":"that we associate with brain function."},{"time":326928,"text":"It can learn, it can remember,"},{"time":328836,"text":"it can solve problems, it can make decisions."},{"time":331593,"text":"So where does that intelligence lie?"},{"time":334308,"text":"So this is a microscopy, a video I shot,"},{"time":336800,"text":"and it's about 100 times magnification,"},{"time":339453,"text":"sped up about 20 times,"},{"time":342320,"text":"and inside the slime mold,"},{"time":344106,"text":"there is a rhythmic pulsing flow,"},{"time":347548,"text":"a vein-like structure carrying"},{"time":349716,"text":"cellular material, nutrients and chemical information"},{"time":353488,"text":"through the cell,"},{"time":355346,"text":"streaming first in one direction\nand then back in another."},{"time":358964,"text":"And it is this continuous, synchronous oscillation"},{"time":362781,"text":"within the cell that allows it to form"},{"time":365037,"text":"quite a complex understanding of its environment,"},{"time":368019,"text":"but without any large-scale control center."},{"time":371388,"text":"This is where its intelligence lies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373969,"text":"So it's not just academic researchers"},{"time":377213,"text":"in universities that are interested in this organism."},{"time":379857,"text":"A few years ago, I set up SliMoCo,"},{"time":382730,"text":"the Slime Mould Collective."},{"time":385070,"text":"It's an online, open, democratic network"},{"time":388293,"text":"for slime mold researchers and enthusiasts"},{"time":390389,"text":"to share knowledge and experimentation"},{"time":393118,"text":"across disciplinary divides"},{"time":396086,"text":"and across academic divides."},{"time":399781,"text":"The Slime Mould Collective\nmembership is self-selecting."},{"time":403221,"text":"People have found the collective"},{"time":406017,"text":"as the slime mold finds the oats."},{"time":409715,"text":"And it comprises of scientists"},{"time":411408,"text":"and computer scientists and researchers"},{"time":412967,"text":"but also artists like me,"},{"time":415254,"text":"architects, designers, writers, activists, you name it."},{"time":420346,"text":"It's a very interesting, eclectic membership."},{"time":424529,"text":"Just a few examples:"},{"time":425866,"text":"an artist who paints with fluorescent Physarum;"},{"time":428991,"text":"a collaborative team"},{"time":430563,"text":"who are combining biological and electronic design"},{"time":434341,"text":"with 3D printing technologies in a workshop;"},{"time":437486,"text":"another artist who is using the slime mold"},{"time":439620,"text":"as a way of engaging a community"},{"time":441720,"text":"to map their area."},{"time":444724,"text":"Here, the slime mold is being used directly"},{"time":446886,"text":"as a biological tool, but metaphorically"},{"time":449764,"text":"as a symbol for ways of talking"},{"time":451748,"text":"about social cohesion, communication"},{"time":455602,"text":"and cooperation."},{"time":457466,"text":"Other public engagement activities,"},{"time":459976,"text":"I run lots of slime mold workshops,"},{"time":461994,"text":"a creative way of engaging with the organism."},{"time":464456,"text":"So people are invited to come and learn"},{"time":466140,"text":"about what amazing things it can do,"},{"time":468036,"text":"and they design their own petri dish experiment,"},{"time":470682,"text":"an environment for the slime mold to navigate"},{"time":472998,"text":"so they can test its properties."},{"time":474636,"text":"Everybody takes home a new pet"},{"time":477080,"text":"and is invited to post their results"},{"time":480020,"text":"on the Slime Mould Collective."},{"time":482438,"text":"And the collective has enabled me"},{"time":483886,"text":"to form collaborations"},{"time":486248,"text":"with a whole array of interesting people."},{"time":488841,"text":"I've been working with filmmakers"},{"time":490434,"text":"on a feature-length slime mold documentary,"},{"time":493900,"text":"and I stress feature-length,"},{"time":496558,"text":"which is in the final stages of edit"},{"time":498267,"text":"and will be hitting your cinema screens very soon."},{"time":501293,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":502773,"text":"It's also enabled me to conduct what I think is"},{"time":506108,"text":"the world's first human slime mold experiment."},{"time":508981,"text":"This is part of an exhibition in Rotterdam last year."},{"time":511953,"text":"We invited people to become\nslime mold for half an hour."},{"time":516644,"text":"So we essentially tied people together"},{"time":519985,"text":"so they were a giant cell,"},{"time":522309,"text":"and invited them to follow slime mold rules."},{"time":525153,"text":"You have to communicate through oscillations,"},{"time":528584,"text":"no speaking."},{"time":529880,"text":"You have to operate as one entity, one mass cell,"},{"time":534813,"text":"no egos,"},{"time":536397,"text":"and the motivation for moving"},{"time":538982,"text":"and then exploring the environment"},{"time":540890,"text":"is in search of food."},{"time":542789,"text":"So a chaotic shuffle ensued\nas this bunch of strangers"},{"time":546420,"text":"tied together with yellow ropes\nwearing \"Being Slime Mold\" t-shirts"},{"time":550328,"text":"wandered through the museum park."},{"time":553284,"text":"When they met trees, they had to reshape"},{"time":556610,"text":"their connections and reform as a mass cell"},{"time":559742,"text":"through not speaking."},{"time":563729,"text":"This is a ludicrous experiment in many, many ways."},{"time":567087,"text":"This isn't hypothesis-driven."},{"time":569036,"text":"We're not trying to prove, demonstrate anything."},{"time":571479,"text":"But what it did provide us was a way"},{"time":573613,"text":"of engaging a broad section of the public"},{"time":575961,"text":"with ideas of intelligence, agency, autonomy,"},{"time":580392,"text":"and provide a playful platform"},{"time":582721,"text":"for discussions about"},{"time":586453,"text":"the things that ensued."},{"time":588837,"text":"One of the most exciting things"},{"time":591170,"text":"about this experiment"},{"time":594030,"text":"was the conversation that happened afterwards."},{"time":596217,"text":"An entirely spontaneous symposium\nhappened in the park."},{"time":600040,"text":"People talked about the human psychology,"},{"time":602069,"text":"of how difficult it was to let go"},{"time":603726,"text":"of their individual personalities and egos."},{"time":607035,"text":"Other people talked about bacterial communication."},{"time":610218,"text":"Each person brought in their own"},{"time":612197,"text":"individual interpretation,"},{"time":615054,"text":"and our conclusion from this experiment was that"},{"time":616959,"text":"the people of Rotterdam were highly cooperative,"},{"time":620865,"text":"especially when given beer."},{"time":623661,"text":"We didn't just give them oats."},{"time":625627,"text":"We gave them beer as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627189,"text":"But they weren't as efficient as the slime mold,"},{"time":629383,"text":"and the slime mold, for me,"},{"time":631367,"text":"is a fascinating subject matter."},{"time":633736,"text":"It's biologically fascinating,"},{"time":635593,"text":"it's computationally interesting,"},{"time":637177,"text":"but it's also a symbol,"},{"time":639251,"text":"a way of engaging with ideas of community,"},{"time":642909,"text":"collective behavior, cooperation."},{"time":646563,"text":"A lot of my work draws on the scientific research,"},{"time":648689,"text":"so this pays homage to the maze experiment"},{"time":651873,"text":"but in a different way."},{"time":653455,"text":"And the slime mold is also my working material."},{"time":655813,"text":"It's a coproducer of photographs, prints, animations,"},{"time":661030,"text":"participatory events."},{"time":662629,"text":"Whilst the slime mold doesn't choose"},{"time":664977,"text":"to work with me, exactly,"},{"time":666883,"text":"it is a collaboration of sorts."},{"time":669485,"text":"I can predict certain behaviors"},{"time":671577,"text":"by understanding how it operates,"},{"time":673633,"text":"but I can't control it."},{"time":675363,"text":"The slime mold has the final say"},{"time":676947,"text":"in the creative process."},{"time":679078,"text":"And after all, it has its own internal aesthetics."},{"time":682567,"text":"These branching patterns that we see"},{"time":684371,"text":"we see across all forms, scales of nature,"},{"time":686921,"text":"from river deltas to lightning strikes,"},{"time":689721,"text":"from our own blood vessels to neural networks."},{"time":693757,"text":"There's clearly significant rules at play"},{"time":696220,"text":"in this simple yet complex organism,"},{"time":698485,"text":"and no matter what our disciplinary\nperspective or our mode of inquiry,"},{"time":702277,"text":"there's a great deal that we can learn"},{"time":704060,"text":"from observing and engaging"},{"time":705829,"text":"with this beautiful, brainless blob."}]},{"cues":[{"time":708950,"text":"I give you Physarum polycephalum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712165,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713918,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}